{"tid":1380514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武前線防線戰術建議","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T02:29:37.000Z","uid":292783,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a9316161112ec9416ed29a0dda62fbb1877fbb6","tid":1380514,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:47:52.000Z","msg":"我想講大家既佈防已經好好 <br />\n只係一個猛攻就要被逼棄左佢<br />\n所以幾堅固都無用<br />\n玩過塔game既bro其實可以試下打斜放欄留位<br />\n推林個欄其實佔既面積仲大 <br />\n因為我地唔會快攻<br />\n對邊快攻一定會比地面既雜物kick親(even a 水樽🤷&zwj;♂️)<br />\n呢個咁既陣唔使縛實亦可動性大<br />\n況且太多邊位佢地衝過黎<br />\n防線只係拖慢對方到達時間<br />\n中間留摩西紅海係需要for走果陣有位<br />\n慢退前線好蝕<br />\n唔好太逼 唔好太逼 唔好太逼<br />\n你推林左10個欄好過縛個三角陣<br />\n講真三角陣你地有幾多次推到狗前?<br />\n仲有目的建防線做前線係乜<br />\n勇武係前面個目的只係對付前面幾十個防暴<br />\n唔攻過去 對面攻又硬食少幾件<br />\n對面又無傷 少左50個其實唔抵<br />\n一係殺出條路 一係有目的係佔路定係點 因為而家已經唔會佔到第二日影響交通壓力 磨時間只會更蝕 <br />\n對面用鎗<br />\n仲有時間越耐 回程各地鐵有狗 退完都比人周<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GvoMpFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvoMpFY.jpg&h=3d69fad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZJ03rUf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZJ03rUf.jpg&h=5e0cb1ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUpvRkX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUpvRkX.jpg&h=357a2d71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ce2ee12fc8bfd0e7961c87d1179bb9c52e00e36","tid":1380514,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:49:12.000Z","msg":"up<br />\n第三張係我地而家用緊既平排兩層防線"},{"pid":"4bbb07e8b3bbc94f8de6387869875eef01a0c888","tid":1380514,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"ba3539f37d10078ecded372c48b2fed1908b4fc7","tid":1380514,"uid":12816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba3418578c6939a907c7570fbbddfcb82d4126a","tid":1380514,"uid":292783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:04:16.000Z","msg":"發夢達過陣 唔係電視睇 <br />\n中型巷戰橫街做到<br />\n你睇電影男女主角走難走到條巷永遠掉兩個垃圾袋就走得甩🤷&zwj;♂️😂<br />\n大馬路 花槽太多"},{"pid":"e8713aa1192b4449cbf06c8cc64fcd4b544b6b37","tid":1380514,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:08:03.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"1c34f01a78f2568f07a43a94b6aa494a9f592e18","tid":1380514,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"其實我諗過吳剛師傅倒瀉左搽身既花生油🤫"},{"pid":"a6935a42bc0d550f66360fe16a3d0710e6e04977","tid":1380514,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:17:45.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"519f4dfb52b5ddce35081c033f480d2f5233054b","tid":1380514,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:23:31.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"b1bf8d51eea1c50fd8d66f70e124cff095fd7367","tid":1380514,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:31:22.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"f2e89c9eff52f5140ada00cd6b93d9fdb8a8a523","tid":1380514,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:38:48.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"46019b61856889e1ea774e3aca01088635e5b437","tid":1380514,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:21:49.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"9db559170b7897b67a1dca3658eb7d6c31ed6520","tid":1380514,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:33:03.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"00e50f3b87f9d1fb388fc0325bfebdb27dc52ea8","tid":1380514,"uid":290385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1fa1d14b93e85751fbcc90613f3529714a95c27","tid":1380514,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:33:57.000Z","msg":"（文宣幫手）Now元朗7分鐘 矛頭要指向 <span style=\"color: red;\">